        "subject": "LU-19209 utils: ofd_access_log_reader usage mention log_size",
        "message": "LU-19209 utils: ofd_access_log_reader usage mention log_size\n\nofd access logs are not enabled by default; they are enabled by\nsetting the size of the circular buffer they require.\n\nState this in the usage message of the utility used to read them, and\nin the comment of the source file implementing them, so users need not\nspelunk through code to learn how.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Olaf Faaland <faaland1@llnl.gov>\nChange-Id: I048e53fdf5c91d3302baaec9b0cad275269aa168\nReviewed-on: https://review.whamcloud.com/c/fs/lustre-release/+/60356\nTested-by: jenkins <devops@whamcloud.com>\nTested-by: Maloo <maloo@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Alex Zhuravlev <bzzz@whamcloud.com>\nReviewed-by: Frederick Dilger <fdilger@whamcloud.com>\n"
